Once that the Ruy Lopez knight establishes itself on the f5 square Black often
has no other choice but to trade it for his bishop.} Bg5 23. Bxg5 Nxg5 24. Qg3
{[#]} Bxf5 {This, however, opens the road for the Spanish light-squared bishop
by White and this is everything it needs to get into the game.} ({Otherwise
