57. Rd7+ Kf6 58. Rc7 f4 59. gxf4 Rd2 60. b5 {1-0 (60) Boleslavsky,I-Kotov,A
Moscow 1944 URS-ch [Chekhov,V]}) 13. Nf1 Rfe8 14. Ne3 g6 15. dxe5 dxe5 16. Nh2
Rad8 17. Qf3 Be6 18. Nhg4 Nxg4 19. hxg4 Qc6 20. Qg3 {[%csl Rf5][%cal Re3f5,
