Bxf6 26. Bh6 Rfe8 27. Be4 Qe6 28. Qf3 Qe7 29. Rad1 Bg7 30. Be3 {The bishops
dominate.} Rf8 31. Qh3 $1 {[%cal Re4g6]} Kg8 {[%csl Gg4,Rg8][%cal Gf3h3,Gh3g4]}
32. Qg4 {[%csl Gg4]} Bf6 33. Rxd8 Rxd8 34. Rd1 Nb7 35. Bxb7 $1 {[%csl Rb7]
[%cal Rc7b7] One way to convert the advantage is to regain the pawn and enter
