36. Qxd1 Qxb7 37. Qd6 Kf7 38. Bxc5 h5 ({There is no:} 38... Qe7 39. Qd5+ Qe6
40. Qb7+ Kg8 41. Qb8+ Kg7 42. Qf8#) 39. c4 bxc4 40. bxc4 Qb1+ 41. Kh2 Qb7 42.
Be3 $16 {Thanks to his more active pieces and the outside passer White is
calling the shots.} e4 43. c5 Be7 44. Qb6 Qd5 45. c6 Bd6+ 46. g3 h4 47. c7
hxg3+ 48. Kg2 Qd1 49. Qxd6 Qxd6 50. c8=Q gxf2 51. Qb7+ Ke6 52. Qxe4+ Kd7 53.
Qb7+ Ke6 54. Qb3+ Kd7 55. Kxf2 Qh2+ 56. Kf3 Qh3+ 57. Ke4 Qf5+ 58. Kd4 Kc6 59.
Kc3 Qe5+ 60. Kc2 Qe4+ 61. Kc1 Kd7 62. Kd2 Qg2+ 63. Kd3 Qc6 64. Kd4 Qf6+ 65. Kc4
Qc6+ 66. Kd3 Qb5+ 67. Kd4 Qc6 68. Bf4 Qf6+ 69. Ke3 Qc6 70. Kd4 Qf6+ 71. Be5
Qf2+ 72. Kd5 Qf7+ 73. Kc5 Qe7+ 74. Kd4 Qh4+ 75. Kd5 Qh1+ 76. Kc5 Qc1+ 77. Kb4
Qc6 78. Qf7+ Kc8 79. Qf8+ Kd7 80. Qc5 g5 81. a4 a5+ 82. Qxa5 Qe4+ 83. Ka3 Qe3+
84. Bc3 Qc1+ 85. Kb3 Qb1+ 86. Ka3 Qc1+ 87. Kb4 Qb1+ 88. Kc5 Qg1+ 89. Kb5 g4 90.
